title: Beethoven Symphonies (J.E. Gardiner)
description:
BEETHOVEN: 9 Symphonies
Performed by the Orchestre Revolutionnaire et Romantique
under the direction of John Eliot Gardiner

Released as a box set by Deutsche Grammophon in 1995

This is a FLAC rip of that box set
Files tagged to indicate opus number, tempo indications, etc.

5 CDs

"Historically informed performances on period instruments"

A very well-regarded set even if the Fifth is taken a little too quickly for my taste. The performance of the Seventh symphony is phenomenal. Play it loud! This is not background music for your doctor's office!
